PrecisReappointment of LINDA YVONNE IVANY of Fall River, Nova Scotia, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Nova Scotia, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective November 1, 2002.
